# import the data 
df = read.csv("quarterly.csv")
dates <- df[,1]
dates <- as.Date.character(dates,format = "%m/%d/%Y")
names(df)[1] <- "DATE"
df[,1] <- dates

x_raw <- df$GDPC1
x = x_raw[!is.na(x_raw)]

hp = BoostedHP(x, lambda=1600, iter = F)
## conducted the simple HP filter
cycle_HP = hp$cycle
tmp = x_raw
tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_HP
cycle_HP = tmp 


bhp.bic = BoostedHP(x, lambda=1600, iter = TRUE, test_type =  "BIC", Max_Iter = 200)
## iterated HP filter with BIC criterion
cycle_BIC = bhp.bic$cycle
tmp = x_raw
tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_BIC
cycle_BIC = tmp 



reg = dynlm( as.ts(x)  ~ L(as.ts(x), c(1:4) ) )
d4 = c( rep(NA,4), predict(reg) )
cycle_AR4 <- x - d4 
tmp = x_raw
tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_AR4
cycle_AR4 = as.numeric(tmp)  


dcycle_GDP <- df[,c("DATE","GDPC1")]
names(dcycle_GDP) <- c("DATE","GDP")
dcycle_GDP$BIC <- cycle_BIC
dcycle_GDP$AR4 <- cycle_AR4
dcycle_GDP$HP <- cycle_HP
#Load the required packages for the graph


graph_fun <- function(series_df, recess_df)  {
  ggp = ggplot(series_df, aes(x = DATE, y = GDP )) + geom_point( )
  
  if (colnames(series_df[2]) == "HP" ){
    ggp = ggp + geom_line(aes(x = DATE, y =  GDP - HP ), color = "red", size = 1, alpha=0.9 )
  } else if ( (colnames(series_df[2]) == "BIC" ) ){
    ggp = ggp + geom_line(aes(x = DATE, y =  GDP - BIC ), color = "blue", size = 1, alpha=0.9 )
  } else if ((colnames(series_df[2]) == "AR4" )){
    ggp = ggp + geom_line(aes(x = DATE, y =  GDP - AR4 ), color = "purple", size = 1, alpha=0.9 )
  }
  
  ggp = ggp + xlab("")+ ylab("") + 
    scale_x_date(date_breaks = "5 years", date_minor_breaks = "1 year", 
                 date_labels = "%Y", limits = as.Date(c("1959-01-01","2022-03-01")))
  ggp = ggp + annotate("rect",xmin = as.Date(recession_1959.df$start, "%Y-%m-%d"),
                       xmax= as.Date(recession_1959.df$end, "%Y-%m-%d"),
                       ymin=-Inf,ymax=Inf, alpha=0.2, fill="black") 
  
  # browser()
  if ( recess_df[1,1] < "1990-01-01" ) {
    ggp = ggp + scale_x_date(date_breaks = "5 year", date_minor_breaks = "1 year", date_labels= "%Y")
  } else {
    ggp = ggp + scale_x_date(date_breaks = "1 year", date_minor_breaks = "1 year", date_labels= "%Y" )
  }
  ggp = ggp + theme_bw()+ theme(legend.position = "none",
                                axis.text=element_text(size=16))
  
  return(ggp)
}

# Quarterly Data 

rm(list = ls() )

source("Rscripts/BoostedHP.R")

# import the data 
df = read.csv("quarterly.csv")
dates <- df[,1]
dates <- as.Date.character(dates,format = "%m/%d/%Y")
names(df)[1] <- "DATE"
df[,1] <- dates

## initialization 
var_names <- colnames(df)
df_HP = df 
df_BIC = df
df_AR4 = df 

i = 1
for (name in var_names[2:length(var_names)]){
  cat("The ", i, "th series is", name, "\n" )
  i <- i + 1
  
  x_raw = df[,name]
  x = x_raw[!is.na(x_raw)]
  
  hp = BoostedHP(x, lambda=1600, iter = F)
  cycle_HP = hp$cycle
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_HP
  cycle_HP = tmp   
  
  bhp.bic = BoostedHP(x, lambda=1600, iter = TRUE, test_type =  "BIC", Max_Iter = 200)
  cycle_BIC = bhp.bic$cycle
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_BIC
  cycle_BIC = tmp   
  
  reg = dynlm( as.ts(x)  ~ L(as.ts(x), c(1:4) ) )
  d4 = c( rep(NA,4), predict(reg) )
  cycle_AR4 <- x - d4 
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_AR4
  cycle_AR4 = as.numeric(tmp) 
  
  df_HP[,name] <- cycle_HP 
  df_BIC[,name] <- cycle_BIC 
  df_AR4[,name] <- cycle_AR4
}

### Generating Cycles 

############## Monthly Data 

rm(list = ls() )

source("Rscripts/BoostedHP.R")

# import the data 
df = read.csv("monthly.csv")
dates <- df[,1]
dates <- as.Date.character(dates,format = "%m/%d/%Y")
names(df)[1] <- "DATE"
df[,1] <- dates



## initialization 
var_names <- colnames(df)
df_HP = df 
df_BIC = df
df_AR4 = df 

i = 1
for (name in var_names[2:length(var_names)]){
  cat("The ", i, "th series is", name, "\n" )
  i <- i + 1
  
  
  x_raw = df[,name]
  x = x_raw[!is.na(x_raw)]
  
  hp = BoostedHP(x, lambda=129600, iter = F)
  cycle_HP = hp$cycle
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_HP
  cycle_HP = tmp 
  
  
  bhp.bic = BoostedHP(x, lambda=129600, iter = TRUE, test_type =  "BIC", Max_Iter = 200)
  cycle_BIC = bhp.bic$cycle
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_BIC
  cycle_BIC = tmp 
  
  
  
  reg = dynlm( as.ts(x)  ~ L(as.ts(x), c(1:4) ) )
  d4 = c( rep(NA,4), predict(reg) )
  cycle_AR4 <- x - d4 
  tmp = x_raw
  tmp[!is.na(tmp)] = cycle_AR4
  cycle_AR4 = as.numeric(tmp)
  
  df_HP[,name] <- cycle_HP 
  df_BIC[,name] <- cycle_BIC 
  df_AR4[,name] <- cycle_AR4
}
